WEBVTT

00:01:57.645 --> 00:02:00.675
ular insonlarga umid va qadrini
ham singdirishi kerak.

00:02:00.699 --> 00:02:02.807
Shu tarzda, kichik ko'mak bilan

00:02:02.831 --> 00:02:05.277
odamlar o'zlarini qashshoqlikdan
olib chiqadi.

00:02:05.737 --> 00:02:09.128
BRAC bitiruv yondashuvini
olbi kirdi,

00:02:09.152 --> 00:02:13.233
o'ta qashshoqlikka yechim sifatida,
u kam daromadni ham,

00:02:13.257 --> 00:02:14.979
umidsizlikni ham o'z ichiga olardi.

00:02:15.487 --> 00:02:17.883
Bu yondashun asosan ayollarga 
tog'ri keladi.

00:02:17.907 --> 00:02:21.141
Chunki ular o'ta qashshoqlikdan
eng ko'p aziyat chekkan.

00:02:21.165 --> 00:02:24.504
Lekin ular o'zlarni va oilalarini
undan olib chiqib

00:02:24.528 --> 00:02:25.680
keta olishadi ham.

00:02:25.704 --> 00:02:27.337
Ikki yil davomida,

00:02:27.361 --> 00:02:29.428
biz asosan to'rtta ish qildik.

00:02:29.769 --> 00:02:32.989
Birinchisi, ayollarning eng asosiy 
ehtiyojlarini qondirdik,